  3.807372939687728*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"079a1083-911e-44ec-b572-\
c76d5d035f7c"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "introduce the idea of ",
 StyleBox["quantized",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " states, meaning that a variable (for example, the energy) can only take on \
certain values."
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.807372959293992*^9, 3.807373032864848*^9}, {
