Cell["\<\
recall the wave/particle duality for both light and matter, as developed by \
Einstein and de Broglie, respectively.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8064070512118487`*^9, 3.8064071296108913`*^9}, {
  3.8064085319006467`*^9, 3.806408589657423*^9}, {3.8064086221967144`*^9, 
